text: Julia Glushko and Alexandra Panova were the defending champions, but both players chose not to participate. Emina Bektas and Sanaz Marand won the title, defeating Kristie Ahn and Lizette Cabrera in the final, 6–3, 1–6, [10–2]. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== *Main Draw Hardee's Pro Classic - Doubles
